        <updateDate>2021-04-22T16:46:23Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Sunshine Protection Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill makes daylight saving time the new, permanent standard time.</p> <p>States with areas exempt from daylight saving time may choose the standard time for those areas.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>55</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2022-03-15</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Passed Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2022-03-17T14:21:19Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Sunshine Protection Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill makes daylight saving time the new, permanent standard time, effective November 5, 2023.</p> <p>States with areas exempt from daylight saving time may choose the standard time for those areas.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
